msgstr "按一下 :guilabel:`目標聯絡人` 欄位，然後從下拉式清單中，選擇其中一個選項。此欄位預設設為系統內最先建立的聯絡人記錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:42
msgid ""
"After confirming the information on the pop-up window, click "
