msgstr ":guilabel:`外部識別碼` （ID）是資料行項目的唯一標識符。為了使你能順利轉用 Odoo，請隨意使用之前軟件中的識別碼。"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:174
msgid ""
"Setting an ID is not mandatory when importing, but it helps in many cases:"
